fields.title: Avengers: Endgame
fields.review: Masterpiece of the Marvel Universe where the earth mightiest hero known as The Avengers must stop Thanos's quest to wipe out half of the universe.

fields.title: Rush Hour
fields.review: A very funny movie about two cops from a different nation saving a little girl from kidnapping and they must work together even though they have different beliefs.

fields.title: KKN di Desa Penari
fields.review: An Indonesian horror movie adopted from twitter where college students must perform community service program deep within a village in East Java where they encounter many strange things.

fields.review: The sequel for The Amazing Spider-man where the Spider-Man must fight his own friend at work while trying to save the population and other plot twist.

fields.review: A movie about an average-on-the-surface couple who shares the same undercover line of work where each one of them was tasked to kill each other.

fields.title: John Wick: Chapter 3 - Parabellum

fields.review: A comedy movie about an agent who returns from training to carry out his missions to prevent the murder of someone important.
